Mike,


I work for Enron Transportation and Storage in their Storage Marketing

group.  My group has been using technical analysis from your website to help

make daily storage trading revenue decisions.  On your web site, you

indicated you would be discontinueing some of the information we use.  We had

interviewed external technical service profiders, and chose not to buy their

service because we had your information available to us to help us make

financial decisions.  Specifically, we need the candlestick charts and

analysis on natural gas, and we also need the elliot wave analysis on natural

gas.


Can you please reconsider your decision to discontinue the technical analysis

data aforementioned?


Sue Neville

Director, Storage Marketing

